`website/web/static/js/dashboard.js`:

```js
let chart = null;
let selectedDate = "";
let onErrorTrigger;

function OnPeriodChange(){
    const selectElement = document.querySelector('#period');
    selectElement.addEventListener('change', (event) => {
        let minViewMode = 2;
        let format = "yyyy"
        if(selectElement.value == "month"){
            minViewMode = 1;
             format = "mm/yyyy"
        }else if(selectElement.value == "day"){
            minViewMode = 0;
            format ="dd/mm/yyyy"
        }else if (selectElement.value == "week") {
            minViewMode = 0;
            format ="dd/mm/yyyy"
        }

        // Destroy previous datepicker
        $('#stats-container #date-picker').datepicker('destroy');
        // Re-int with new options
        initDatePicker(minViewMode, format)
    });
}

function getEndDate(){
    const today = new Date()
    const tomorrow = new Date(today)
    tomorrow.setDate(today.getDate() + 1)
    return tomorrow.toISOString()
}

function initDatePicker(minViewMode,format) {
    $('#stats-container #date-picker').datepicker({
        format: format,
        endDate: getEndDate(),
        startView: 2,
        minViewMode: minViewMode,
        maxViewMode: 2,
        orientation: "bottom auto",
        calendarWeeks: true,
        autoclose: true,
        setDate: new Date(),
    }).on('hide',  (ev) => {
        const period = $("#period").val()
        if(ev.date) {
            const dateSel = new Date(ev.date)
            if (period == "week") {
                const mDate = moment(dateSel);
                $('#date-picker').val(`Week ${mDate.isoWeek()} of ${mDate.year()}`);
                updateData(chart, `${mDate.isoWeek()}/${mDate.year()}`);
                return
            }
            updateData(chart);
            selectedDate = $("#date-picker").val()
        }else {
            $("#date-picker").val(selectedDate)
        }
    })
    const today = moment(new Date())
    const period = $("#period").val()
    if(period == "week"){
        $('#date-picker').val(`Week ${today.isoWeek()} of ${today.year()}`);
        updateData(chart, `${today.isoWeek()}/${today.year()}`);
    } else{
        $('#date-picker').val(today.format(format.toUpperCase()));
        updateData(chart);
    }
    selectedDate = $("#date-picker").val()
}


function initChart(data) {
    'use strict'

    // Graphs
    const ctx = document.getElementById('submit-chart')

    // eslint-disable-next-line no-unused-vars
     chart = new Chart(ctx, {
        type: 'line',
        data: {
            labels: data.labels,
            datasets: [{
                data: data.values,
                lineTension: 0.1,
                backgroundColor: 'transparent',
                borderColor: '#009697',
                borderWidth: 4,
                pointBackgroundColor: '#009697'
            }]
        }
    })
}

function updateChart(labels, values){
    chart.data.labels = labels
    chart.data.datasets[0].data = values
    chart.update()
}

function removeData(chart) {
    chart.data.labels = []
    chart.data.datasets[0].data = []
    chart.update();
}


function updateData(chart, selected){
    const period = $("#period").val()
    if(!selected) {
        selected =  $('#date-picker').val()
    }
    getSubmit(period, selected)
    getInfos(period, selected)

}

function updateSubmitInfos(infos){
    const tbody = $('#submit-infos .table tbody')
    $("#submit-infos .table tbody tr").remove();
    Object.keys(infos).forEach(key => {
        if(key != "total") {
            const newRowContent = `<tr><td>${key}</td><td>${infos[key]}</td></tr>`
            tbody.append(newRowContent);
        }
    })
    if(infos.total != undefined){
        tbody.append(`<tr><td><B>Total</B></td><td><b>${infos.total}</b></td></tr>`);
    }
}

function updateFilesInfos(infos){
    $("#files-info .table tbody tr").remove();
    const tbody = $('#files-info .table tbody')
    Object.keys(infos).sort(function(a, b) {
        return infos[a] - infos[b]
    }).reverse().forEach(key => {
        if(key != "total") {
            const newRowContent = `<tr><td>${key}</td><td>${infos[key]}</td></tr>`
            tbody.append(newRowContent);
        }
    })
    if(infos.total  != undefined){
        tbody.append(`<tr><td><B>Total</B></td><td><b>${infos.total}</b></td></tr>`);
    }
}

function updateSizeInfos(infos){
    const tr = $('#files-size-info .table tbody tr')
    $("#files-size-info .table tbody tr td").remove();
    tr.append(`<td>${infos.min}</td>`);
    tr.append(`<td>${infos.max}</td>`);
    tr.append(`<td>${infos.avg}</td>`);
}

function updateInterval(start, end){
    $('#interval-info .start-date').text(start)
    $('#interval-info .end-date').text(end)
}

function updateMetrics(metrics){
    const ratioDiv = $("#alert-ratio")
    const ratioMetric = $("#alert-ratio .metric")
    const totalMetrics = $("#total-submits .metric")
    const maliciousMetric = $("#malicious-submits .metric")
    const suspiciousMetric = $("#suspicious-submits .metric")
    const overwrittenMetric = $("#overwritten-submits .metric")
    const errorMetric = $("#error-submits .metric")
    const cleanMetric = $("#clean-submits .metric")
    ratioDiv.removeClass()

    const nbf = Intl.NumberFormat("en",{ notation: "compact" , compactDisplay: "short" })
    ratioMetric.text(nbf.format(metrics.alert_ratio))
    maliciousMetric.text(nbf.format(metrics.malicious))
    suspiciousMetric.text(nbf.format(metrics.suspicious))
    overwrittenMetric.text(nbf.format(metrics.overwritten))
    errorMetric.text(nbf.format(metrics.error))
    cleanMetric.text(nbf.format(metrics.clean))
    totalMetrics.text(nbf.format(metrics.submits))

    if(metrics.alert_ratio > 80){
        ratioDiv.addClass("ratio-alert")
    }else if (metrics.alert_ratio > 50){
        ratioDiv.addClass("ratio-warn")
    }else{
        ratioDiv.addClass("ratio-okay")
    }
}

function previousDate(){
    const period = $("#period").val()
    let selected =  $('#date-picker').val()
    const today = moment()
    let toShow = selected
    if(period == "year"){
        const pattern = "YYYY"
        let mDate = moment(selected,pattern)
        if(mDate < today){
            enableNext()
        }
        mDate = mDate.subtract(1, 'year')
        selected = mDate.format(pattern)
        toShow = selected
    }else if(period == "month"){
        const pattern = "MM/YYYY"
        let mDate = moment(selected,pattern)
        if(mDate < today){
            enableNext()
        }
        mDate = mDate.subtract(1, 'months')
        selected = mDate.format(pattern)
        toShow = selected
    }else if(period == "week"){
        const pattern = "Week WW of YYYY"
        const week = selected.split(" ")[1]
        const year = selected.split(" ")[3]
        if(week == 53){
            toShow = `Week 52 of ${year}`
            selected = `52/${year}`
        }else{
            let mDate = moment(selected,pattern)
            if(mDate < today){
                enableNext()
            }
            mDate = mDate.subtract(7,"days")
            toShow = `Week ${mDate.isoWeek()} of ${mDate.year()}`
            selected = mDate.format("WW/YYYY")
        }
    }else if(period == "day"){
        let pattern = "DD/MM/YYYY"
        let mDate = moment(selected,pattern)
        if(mDate < today){
            enableNext()
        }
        mDate = mDate.subtract(1, 'days')
        selected = mDate.format(pattern)
        toShow = selected
    }
    $('#date-picker').val(toShow)
    updateData(chart, selected)
}


function nextDate(){
    const period = $("#period").val()
    let selected =  $('#date-picker').val()
    let toShow = ""
    const today = moment()
    if(period == "year"){
        const pattern = "YYYY"
        const mDate = moment(selected,pattern).add(1, 'year')
        if(mDate < today) {
            selected = mDate.format(pattern)
            toShow = selected
        }
        if (mDate.add(1,"year") > today){
            disableNext()
        }
    }else if(period == "month"){
        const pattern = "MM/YYYY"
        const mDate = moment(selected,pattern).add(1, 'month')
        if(mDate < today) {
            selected = mDate.format(pattern)
            toShow = selected
        }
        if (mDate.add(1,"month") > today){
            disableNext()
        }
    }else if(period == "week"){
        const pattern = "Week WW of YYYY"
        const mDate =  moment(selected,pattern).add(1,"week")
        if(mDate < today) {
            toShow = `Week ${mDate.isoWeek()} of ${mDate.year()}`
            selected = mDate.format("WW/YYYY")
        }
        if (mDate.add(1,"week") > today){
            disableNext()
        }
    }else if(period == "day"){
        let pattern = "DD/MM/YYYY"
        const mDate = moment(selected,pattern).add(1, 'day')
        if(mDate < today) {
            selected = mDate.format(pattern)
            toShow = selected
        }
        if (mDate.add(1,"day") > today){
            disableNext()
        }
    }
    if(toShow) {
        $('#date-picker').val(toShow)
        updateData(chart, selected)
    }
}

function disableNext(){
    $("#next-date").addClass("disabled")
}
function enableNext(){
    $("#next-date").removeClass("disabled");
}


function onError(error){
    onErrorTrigger = true;
    $("#stats-container").hide()
    $("#error-stats-container .error").text(error)
    $("#error-stats-container").show()
}

initDatePicker(2,"yyyy");
OnPeriodChange();
disableNext()

```

`website/web/static/js/render_tables.js`:

```js
"use strict";

function render_datetime_with_tz(data) {
    if(! isNaN(data)){
        data = parseInt(data);
    }
    const date = new Date(data);
    return `${date.getFullYear()}-${(date.getMonth() + 1).toString().padStart(2, "0")}-${date.getDate().toString().padStart(2, "0")} ${date.toTimeString()}`;
};

DataTable.render.datetime_with_tz = function () {
    return function ( data, type, row ) {
        if ( type === 'display' || type === 'filter') {
            return render_datetime_with_tz(data);
        }
        return data;
    };
}

function renderTables() {
    if (document.getElementById('TasksTable')) {
        let csrf_token = document.getElementById('TasksTable').dataset.csrf;
        new DataTable('#TasksTable', {
          processing: true,
          serverSide: true,
          retrieve: true,
          ordering: false,
          searching: true,
          order: [[ 2, "desc" ]],
          ajax: {
            url: `/tables/tasksTable/${window.location.search}`,
            type: 'POST',
            headers: {"X-CSRF-Token" : csrf_token}
          },
          columns : [
              { data: 'id', width: '10%' },
              { data: 'owner', width: '5%' },
              { data: 'date', width: '15%', render: DataTable.render.datetime_with_tz() },
              { data: {_: 'status.display', filter: 'status.filter'}, width: '5%' },
              { data: {_: 'name.display', filter: 'name.filter'}, width: '40%' },
              { data: 'sha256', width: '15%' },
              { data: {_: 'buttons.display', filter: 'buttons.filter'}, width: '10%' }
          ],
        })
    }
}

document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    renderTables();
});

```

`website/web/static/js/role.js`:

```js
function Role(CSRFToken, updateURL, reloadURL) {
    this.CSRFToken = CSRFToken;
    this.updateURL = updateURL;
    this.reloadURL = reloadURL;
}

Role.prototype.update = function (roleName, permission, value) {
    fetch(this.updateURL, {
      method: "POST",
      headers: {
        "X-CSRF-Token": this.CSRFToken,
        'Content-Type': 'application/json'
      },
      body: JSON.stringify({role_name: roleName, permission: permission, value: value})
    })
    .then(response => response.json())
    .then(data => {
      if (data.success === false) {
        throw new Error(data.error);
      }
      $(`#true-${roleName}-${permission}`).toggleClass("d-none");
      $(`#false-${roleName}-${permission}`).toggleClass("d-none");
    })
    .catch((error) => {
      alert("An error has occurred while changing role permission : " + error);
    });
}

Role.prototype.reload = function () {
    if (!confirm("All the roles will be removed and re-created, are you sure that your config file is correctly formatted ?")) {
        return false;
    }
    fetch(this.reloadURL, {
        method: "POST",
        headers: {
          "X-CSRF-Token": this.CSRFToken
        }
    })
    .then(response => response.json())
    .then(data => {
      if (data.success === false) {
        throw new Error(data.error);
      }
      window.location.reload();
    })
    .catch((error) => {
      alert("An error has occurred while reloading roles from config file : " + error);
    });
}

```

`website/web/static/js/stats.js`:

```js
let submitLoading = true
let submitEnding = false
let statsLoading = false
let statsEnding = false

function getSubmit(period, selected){
    const url = formatUrl("/api/stats/submit", period, selected)
    //Fetch data
    $.ajax({
        url: url,
        dataType:"json",
        async: true,
        success: (data) => {
            if(data.success != undefined && !data.success){
                onError(data.error)
            }
            updateInterval(data.date_start, data.date_end)

            let labels = {}
            let values = {}
            if(period == "year"){
                labels = data.sub_months.map(el => moment.months()[el[0]-1])
                values = data.sub_months.map(el => el[1])
            }else if(period == "month"){
                labels = data.sub_weeks.map(el => el[0])
                values = data.sub_weeks.map(el => el[1])
            }else if(period == "week"){
                labels = data.sub_days.map(el => el[0])
                values = data.sub_days.map(el => el[1])
            }else if(period == "day"){
                labels = data.sub_hours.map(el => el[0])
                values = data.sub_hours.map(el => el[1])
            }

            if (chart == null){
                initChart(data)
            }
            updateChart(labels, values)
        },
        error: function(XMLHttpRequest, textStatus, errorThrown) {
            const data = XMLHttpRequest.responseJSON
            if(data && data.success != undefined && !data.success){
                onError(data.error)
            }else {
                onError(`Code ${XMLHttpRequest.status}: ${XMLHttpRequest.statusText}`)
            }
            },
        beforeSend: () =>{
            submitEnding = false

            setTimeout(() => {
                if(!submitEnding) {
                    submitLoading = true;
                    $("#loading-stats-container").show();
                    $("#stats-container").hide();
                }
            }, 200);
        },
        complete: () => {
            submitEnding = true
            if(submitLoading) {
                $("#loading-stats-container").hide();
                if (!onErrorTrigger) {
                    $("#stats-container").fadeIn(500);
                }
            }
        },
    }).responseText;

}

function getInfos(period, selected){
    const url = formatUrl("/api/stats/", period, selected)
    url.slice(2)
    //Fetch data
    $.ajax({
        url: url,
        dataType:"json",
        async: true,
        error: function(XMLHttpRequest, textStatus, errorThrown) {
            const data = XMLHttpRequest.responseJSON
            if(data && data.success != undefined && !data.success){
                onError(data.error)
            }else {
                onError(`Code ${XMLHttpRequest.status}: ${XMLHttpRequest.statusText}`)
            }
        },
        success: function(data){
            if(data.success != undefined && !data.success){
                onError(data.error)
            }
            updateSubmitInfos(data.submit)
            updateFilesInfos(data.file)
            updateSizeInfos(data.submit_size)
            updateMetrics(data.metrics)
        },
        beforeSend: () =>{
            setTimeout(() => {
                if(!statsEnding) {
                    statsLoading = true;
                    $("#loading-stats-container").show();
                    $("#stats-container").hide();
                }
            }, 200);
        },
        complete: () => {
            statsEnding = true
            if(statsLoading) {
                $("#loading-stats-container").hide();
                if (!onErrorTrigger) {
                    $("#stats-container").fadeIn(500);
                }
            }
        },
    }).responseText;
}

function formatUrl(base, period, selected){
    let url = base
    if(period == "year"){
        url += `/year/${selected}`
    }else if(period == "month"){
        url += `/month/${selected}`
    }else if (period == "week"){
        url += `/week/${selected}`
    }else if (period == "day"){
        url += `/day/${selected}`
    }
    return url
}

```

```js
function getDisabledWorkers(){
```

```html
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="observables" aria-selected=false">
                  Observables&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="badge bg-secondary" id="number_observables">{{ task.observables|length }}</span>

              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#history"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="history" aria-selected=false">
                History&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="badge">{{ task.linked_tasks|length }}</span>
              </button>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Tab panels -->
          <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
           <div class="tab-content">

            <!-- Content preview -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane show active" id="content-preview">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>Content Preview</h3>
                </div>

              <!-- Content preview -->
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12" style="margin-bottom:50px">
                  <!-- Emails -->
                  {% if (task.file.is_msg and task.file.msg_data)
                        or (task.file.is_eml and task.file.eml_data)%}
                  <p class="lead">The information below are extracted from the email,
                      the fields shouldn't be trusted as they can have been
                      tempered with by the sender</p>
                  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered"
                         id="emailContent">
                    <tr>
                      <th style="width:20%">Date</th>
                      <td id="email-date">
                      {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.date %}
                        {{ task.file.msg_data.date }}
                      {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.date %}
                        {{ moment(task.file.eml_data.header.date|to_datetime).format('L LT [UTC]Z') }}
                      {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>From</th>
                      <td id="email-from">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.sender %}
                          {{ task.file.msg_data.sender }}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.from %}
                          {{ task.file.eml_data.header.from }}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>To</th>
                      <td id="email-to">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.recipients %}
                          {% for r in task.file.msg_data.recipients %}
                            {{ r.formatted }}</br>
                          {% endfor %}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.to %}
                          {% for r in task.file.eml_data.header.to %}
                            {{ r }}</br>
                          {% endfor %}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>Subject</th>
                      <td id="email-subject">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.subject %}
                          {{ task.file.msg_data.subject }}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.subject %}
                          {{ task.file.eml_data.header.subject }}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>Hops</th>
                      <td id="email-hops">
                      {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.header.received %}
                        {{ task.file.msg_data.header.received }}
                        {% for received in task.file.msg_data.header.received %}
                        {% endfor %}
                      {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.received %}
                        {% for received in task.file.eml_data.header.received %}
                          {% if 'from' in received %}
                            <span>{{ received.from[0] }}</span> <small class="text-muted">{{ received.from[1] }}</small><br/>
                          {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                      {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Received SPF</th>
                      <td id="received-spf">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.header.get('Received-SPF') %}
                          {{ task.file.msg_data.header['Received-SPF'] }}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.get('header')
                                and task.file.eml_data.header['header'].get('received-spf') %}
                          {{ task.file.eml_data.header['header']['received-spf'] }}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% if current_user.role.can(action.download_images) %}
                    <tr id="email-body">
                      <th>Body</th>
                      <td>
                        <div class="row preview-done {% if not task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}" id="previews_images">
                          {% include 'previews.html' %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="row preview-wait {% if task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                          <div class="img-thumbnail small-status-flag status-flag-error">Content preview is not available</div>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endif %}
                  </table>

                  <!-- Image preview -->
                  {% elif current_user.role.can(action.download_images) %}
                  <div class="row preview-done {% if not task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}" id="previews_images">
                    {% include 'previews.html' %}
                  </div>
                  <div class="row preview-wait {% if task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                    <div class="img-thumbnail small-status-flag status-flag-error">Content preview is not available</div>
                  </div>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if task.file.is_html %}
                    <div class="row">
                    {% if 'lookyloo' in task.reports and 'permaurl' in task.reports['lookyloo'].details %}
                      <a href="{{task.reports['lookyloo'].details['permaurl']}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">See capture on Lookyloo</a>
                    {% elif 'lookyloo' in task.reports and task.reports['lookyloo'].status == status.MANUAL %}
                      This document can probably be opened in a browser,
                      you can submit it to lookyloo and see.
                      Note that as it is sending the sample to a 3rd party service,
                      the module needs to be triggered manually.
                      <a href="{{url_for('manual_trigger_worker', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, worker_name='lookyloo')}}">
                          Click here to do so.
                      </a>
                    {% endif %}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {% if current_user.role.can(action.see_text_preview) %}
              {% if task.file.text %}
              <!-- Text Preview -->
              <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="text-preview-content">
                <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                  <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h3>Text preview</h3>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row preview-done {% if not task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                  <div>The text content can be huge, only display a part of it.</div>
                  <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="img-hover">
                      <a href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='txt_preview') }}" target="_blank">
                        <img class="img-thumbnail" width="70%" src="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='txt_preview') }}">
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row preview-wait {% if task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                  <div>Creating preview, please wait...</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            {% endif %}

            <!-- Text content -->
            {% if current_user.role.can('download_text') and task.file.text %}
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="text-content">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>Text content</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <pre>{{task.file.text}}</pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if task.file.metadata %}
            <!-- File metadata -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="metadata">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>Metadata</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12" style="margin-bottom:50px">
                  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered" >
                  {% for key, value in task.file.metadata.items() %}
                    <tr>
                      <th style="width:30%">{{key}}</th>
                      <td>{{value}}</td>
                    </tr>
                  {% endfor %}
                  </table>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <!-- Observables -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="observables_list">
              <div id="observables_content"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Extracted tasks -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="extracted">
                <div id="extracted_content"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Linked tasks -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane {% if not task.linked_tasks%} d-none {% endif %}" id="history">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>History</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
                  <tr>
                    <th>Date</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                  </tr>
                  {% for linked_task in task.linked_tasks %}
                  <tr class="{% if linked_task.uuid == task.uuid %}active{% endif %}" id="linkedTaskRow-{{ linked_task.uuid }}">
                    <td>
                      {{ moment(linked_task.save_date).format('L LT [UTC]Z') }}
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <a href="{{ url_for('api_analysis', task_id=linked_task.uuid) }}">
                        {{ render_icon(task.file.icon) }}
                        {{ linked_task.file.client_name }}
                      </a>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      {{ display_task_status(task.status, status) }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {% endfor %}
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal notify -->
  {% if current_user.role.can('notify_cert') %}
    <div id="notifyModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <form id="notifyForm" class="form-horizontal" action="{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='notify') }}"
              onsubmit="return analysis.notify($(this).attr('action'))">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h4 class="modal-title">Send message to {{admin_name}}</h4>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4"><span><b>Your email address:</b></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-8"><input style="width:100%" name="email" type="email" id="email" required/></div>
              </div>
              <div class="row" style="margin-top:10px">
                <div class="col-md-4"><span><b>Your message:</b></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-8"><textarea name="message" required rows="10" style="width:100%" id="message"></textarea></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- boat fields -->
            <label class="boatymcboat form-label" for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input class="boatymcboat" autocomplete="off" type="text" id="name" name="name"
                   placeholder="Your fav boat name here">
            <!-- end -->
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10 d-none alert alert-info" id="notifySuccess">Your message has been correctly sent.</div>
              <div class="col-md-10 d-none alert alert-danger" id="notifyError">
                An error has occurred while sending your message:<span id="notifyErrorReason"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Cancel</button>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="notifySubmit">Send message</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Modal share -->
  {% if current_user.role.can('share_analysis') %}
    <div id="shareModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <h4 class="modal-title">Get a URL to share</h4>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <form id="shareForm" class="form-horizontal"
                    action="{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='share') }}"
                    onsubmit="return analysis.share($(this).attr('action'))">
              <div class="row g-3 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-auto">
                  <label for="shareDays" class="col-form-label">URL lifetime:</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                  <input style="width:100px" class="form-control" aria-describedby="shareDaysHelp"
                                                                  id="shareDays" name="number" type="number" min="0" value="{{default_share_time}}" required>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                  <span id="shareDaysHelp" class="form-text">
                    In day(s), 0 means unlimited.
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary" id="shareBuild" style="float: right;">Create a shareable link</button>
              </form>

              </br>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col d-none alert alert-info" id="shareSuccess">
                  This analysis will be available <b><span id="sharePeriod"></span></b> with
                  <a href="" id="shareLink" class="alert-link">this link</a> -
                  <button type="button" class="btn alert-link" style="padding:0"
                          title="Copy to clipboard"
                          onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(shareLink).then(
                                    function() {document.getElementById('copySuccess').classList.remove('d-none')},
                                    function() {document.getElementById('copyError').classList.remove('d-none')})">
                      (copy to clipboard {{ render_icon('clipboard-plus', color='black') }})
                  </button>
                </div>
                <div class="col d-none alert alert-danger" id="shareError">
                  An error has occurred while creating the shareable link:
                  <span id="shareErrorReason"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col d-none alert alert-success" id="copySuccess">
                Shareable link successfully copied to clipboard.
              </div>
              <div class="col d-none alert alert-danger" id="copyError">
                Unable to copy the sharing link to the clipboard.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary d-none" data-bs-dismiss="modal" id="closeBuild">Close</button>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
{% endblock %}

```

`website/web/templates/analysis_fr.html`:

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}
{% from 'bootstrap5/utils.html' import render_icon %}
{% from 'bootstrap5/utils.html' import render_messages %}
{% from "macros.html" import display_task_status %}

{% block title %}
    Pandora - Analysis of {{ task.file.original_filename }}
{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
  {{ super() }}
  <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/analysis.js') }}"
          integrity="{{get_sri('static/js', 'analysis.js')}}"
          crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script>
    var analysis = new Analysis("{{ csrf_token() }}");

    $(document).ready(function () {
      analysis.refresher = setInterval(function() {
        analysis.refresh("{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='refresh') }}");
      }, 1000);
    });
  </script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  {{ render_messages(container=True, dismissible=True) }}
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <!-- Eventual JS Error -->
    <div class="row d-none" id="errorJS">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="alert alert-danger">
          <span id="errorJSInner"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Status Alert -->
    <div class="row" id="taskStatusAlert">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="alert alert-warning {% if not task.file.deleted %} d-none {% endif %}" id="alertDeleted" role="alert">
          <strong>Deleted File! </strong> File and previews are no longer available. Only the stats are displayed.
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-info {% if task.workers_done %} d-none {% endif %}" id="alertPending" role="alert">
          <strong>Pending Task! </strong> Data will be available soon...
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-error {% if task.status != 'ERROR' %} d-none {% endif %}" id="alertFailed" role="alert">
          <strong>Failed Task! </strong> Oops, something really bad happened...
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <!-- Overall column -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <!-- Overall header -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div id="overall-label"><h1>Résultat<br/></h1></div>
          </div>
          {% if current_user.role.can('share_analysis') %}
          <div class="col-sm-4">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin:5px"
                  data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#shareModal">
              Partager l'analyse
          </button>
          </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if current_user.role.can(['rescan_file', 'notify_cert', 'delete_file'], 'or') %}
          <div class="col-sm-2">
            <div class="dropdown" style="margin:5px">
              <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button"
                      id="dropdownMenuActions" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                      aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="true">
                Actions ... <span class="caret"></span>
              </button>
              <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuActions">
              {% if current_user.role.can('rescan_file') and not task.file.deleted %}
                <li>
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="#" onclick="javascript:analysis.rescan($(this).attr('data-url'))"
                     data-url="{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='rescan') }}">
                    Re-analyser le ficher
                  </a>
                </li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if current_user.role.can('notify_cert') %}
                <li>
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#notifyModal">
                      Alerter {{admin_name}}
                  </a>
                </li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if current_user.role.can('delete_file') and not task.file.deleted %}
                  <li id="deleteButton">
                    <a class="dropdown-item" href="#" onclick="javascript:analysis.deleteFile($(this).attr('data-url'))"
                       data-url="{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='delete') }}">
                      Delete file
                    </a>
                  </li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if current_user.role.can('submit_to_misp') and not task.file.deleted %}
                  <li id="submitMISPButton">
                    <a class="dropdown-item"
                       href="{{ url_for('task_misp_submit', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed) }}"
                       title="Submit to MISP">
                      Submit to MISP
                    </a>
                  </li>
              {% endif %}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- Overall status -->
        <div class="row" id="taskStatus">
          <div class="col-md-1"></div>
          {% for s in status %}
          <div class="col-md-4 img-thumbnail overall-status-flag status-flag-{{ s.name|lower }}
               {% if s != task.status %} d-none {% endif %}" id="taskStatusIcon">
            {% if s != status.ALERT %}
              {{ render_icon(status_icons[s]) }}
            {% else %}
              <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='images/skull.svg') }}" width = "160" height = "160">
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          {% endfor %}

          <div class="col-md-6" id="taskStatusMessage">
              <div class="alert alert-overwrite {% if task.status != status.OVERWRITE %}d-none{% endif %}">
                {{ task_status_messages['overwrite'] | safe }}
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-error {% if task.status != status.ERROR %}d-none{% endif %}">
              {{ task_status_messages['error'] | safe }}
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-danger {% if task.status != status.ALERT %}d-none{% endif %}">
              {{ task_status_messages['danger'] | safe }}
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-warning {% if task.status != status.WARN %}d-none{% endif %}">
              {{ task_status_messages['warning'] | safe }}
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-success {% if task.status != status.CLEAN %}d-none{% endif %}">
              {{ task_status_messages['success'] | safe }}
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-info {% if task.workers_done %} d-none {% endif %}">
              {{ task_status_messages['info'] | safe }}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-1"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- File details -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div>
              <h3>File details</h3>
            </div>

            <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
              <tr>
                <th style="width:30%">Name</th>
                <td>{{ render_icon(task.file.icon) }}{{task.file.original_filename}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Submission Date</th>
                <td>{{ moment(task.save_date).format('lll') }}</td>
              </tr>
              {% if task.file.size is not none %}
                <tr>
                  <th>Size</th>
                  <td>{{ sizeof_fmt(task.file.size) }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.parent %}
                <tr>
                  <th>Extracted from</th>
                  <td>{{ render_icon(task.file.icon) }}{{ task.parent.file.original_filename }}
                    <a href="{{ url_for('api_analysis', task_id=task.parent.uuid, seed=seed) }}">
                        <span class="alert-link">See report</span>
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.file.type is not none %}
                <tr>
                  <th>Type</th>
                  <td>{{ task.file.info }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.file.mime_type is not none %}
                <tr>
                  <th>MimeType</th>
                  <td>{{ task.file.mime_type }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.file.encoding %}
                <tr>
                  <th>Encoding</th>
                  <td>{{ task.file.encoding }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.file.md5 is not none %}
                <tr>
                  <th>MD5</th>
                  <td>{{ task.file.md5 }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.file.sha1 is not none %}
                <tr>
                  <th>SHA-1</th>
                  <td>{{ task.file.sha1 }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
              {% if task.file.sha256 is not none %}
                <tr>
                  <th>SHA-256</th>
                  <td style="font-size:smaller">{{ task.file.sha256 }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
            </table>
          </div>
          {% if current_user.detailed_view %}
          <div id="workers_results_overwrite"></div>
          <div id="workers_results_alert"></div>
          <div id="workers_results_warn"></div>
          <div id="workers_results_clean"></div>
          <div id="workers_results_unknown"></div>
          <div id="workers_results_manual"></div>
          <div id="workers_results_error"></div>
          <div hidden id="workers_results_notapplicable"></div>
          <div hidden id="workers_results_disabled"></div>
          {%else%}
          <div class="md-3" onclick="toggle_detailed_view()">
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
              <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" value=""
                     id="detailedView" {% if current_user.detailed_view %}checked{% endif %}>
              <label class="form-check-label" for="detailedView">
                Show details
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tabs column -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="container-fluid">

          <!-- Nav tabs -->
          <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item">
              <button class="nav-link active link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#content-preview"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="content-preview" aria-selected="true">Content preview</button>
            </li>
            {% if current_user.role.can(action.see_text_preview) %}
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item {% if not task.file.text %} d-none {% endif %}">
              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#text-preview-content"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="text-preview-content" aria-selected=false">Text Preview</button>
            </li>
            {% endif %}
            {% if current_user.role.can(action.download_text) %}
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item {% if not task.file.text %} d-none {% endif %}">
              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#text-content"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="text-content" aria-selected=false">Text content</button>
            </li>
            {% endif %}
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item {% if not task.file.metadata%} d-none {% endif %}">
              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#metadata"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="metadata" aria-selected=false">Metadata</button>
            </li>
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item {% if not task.observables %} d-none {% endif %}" id="observables_tab">
              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#observables_list"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="observables" aria-selected=false">
                  Observables&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="badge bg-secondary" id="number_observables">{{ task.observables|length }}</span>
              </button>
            </li>
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item {% if not task.extracted %} d-none {% endif %}" id="extracted_tab">
              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#extracted"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="extracted" aria-selected=false">
                  Extracted&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="badge bg-secondary" id="number_extracted">{{ task.extracted|length }}</span>
              </button>
            </li>
            <li role="presentation" class="nav-item {% if not task.linked_tasks %} d-none {% endif %}">
              <button class="nav-link link-dark"
                      data-bs-toggle="tab"
                      data-bs-target="#history"
                      type="button" role="tab"
                      aria-controls="history" aria-selected=false">
                History&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="badge">{{ task.linked_tasks|length }}</span>
              </button>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Tab panels -->
          <div class="tab-content">

            <!-- Content preview -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane show active" id="content-preview">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>Appercu du contenu</h3>
                </div>

                <!-- Download button -->
                {% if current_user.role.can([action.download_images, action.download_pdf, action.download_zip], 'or')
                      and not task.file.deleted %}
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="dropdown">
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button"
                            id="dropdownMenu1" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="true">
                      Télécharger ... <span class="caret"></span>
                    </button>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenu1">
                      {% if current_user.role.can(action.download_pdf) and task.file.is_pdf %}
                      <!-- TODO: also allow PDF export from office docs, not implemented yet -->
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item"
                             href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='pdf') }}"
                             title="Download pdf">
                          PDF File
                        </a>
                      </li>
                      {% endif %}

                      {% if current_user.role.can(action.download_images) and task.file.previews %}
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item"
                             href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='img') }}"
                             title="Download images">
                          Images
                        </a>
                      </li>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if current_user.role.can(action.download_text) and task.file.text %}
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item"
                             href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='txt') }}"
                             title="Download text">
                          Text
                        </a>
                      </li>
                      {% endif %}

                      {% if current_user.role.can('download_zip') %}
                      <li role="separator" class="divider"></li>
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item"
                           href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='zip') }}"
                           title="Download protected zip file containing sample (password is {{ zip_pass }})">
                         Original sample (password: "{{ zip_passwd }}")
                        </a>
                      </li>
                      {% endif %}

                      {% if current_user.role.can('download_misp') %}
                      <li role="separator" class="divider"></li>
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item"
                           href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='misp') }}"
                           title="Download the analysis in MISP format">
                         Download the analysis in MISP format
                        </a>
                      </li>
                      {% endif %}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>

              <!-- Content preview -->
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12" style="margin-bottom:50px">
                  <!-- Emails -->
                  {% if (task.file.is_msg and task.file.msg_data)
                        or (task.file.is_eml and task.file.eml_data)%}
                  <p class="lead">The information below are extracted from the email,
                      the fields shouldn't be trusted as they can have been
                      tempered with by the sender</p>
                  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered"
                         id="emailContent">
                    <tr>
                      <th style="width:20%">Date</th>
                      <td id="email-date">
                      {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.date %}
                        {{ task.file.msg_data.date }}
                      {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.date %}
                        {{ moment(task.file.eml_data.header.date|to_datetime).format('L LT [UTC]Z') }}
                      {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>From</th>
                      <td id="email-from">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.sender %}
                          {{ task.file.msg_data.sender }}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.from %}
                          {{ task.file.eml_data.header.from }}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>To</th>
                      <td id="email-to">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.recipients %}
                          {% for r in task.file.msg_data.recipients %}
                            {{ r.formatted }}</br>
                          {% endfor %}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.to %}
                          {% for r in task.file.eml_data.header.to %}
                            {{ r }}</br>
                          {% endfor %}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>Subject</th>
                      <td id="email-subject">
                        {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.subject %}
                          {{ task.file.msg_data.subject }}
                        {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.subject %}
                          {{ task.file.eml_data.header.subject }}
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <th>Hops</th>
                      <td id="email-hops">
                      {% if task.file.msg_data and task.file.msg_data.header.received %}
                        {{ task.file.msg_data.header.received }}
                        {% for received in task.file.msg_data.header.received %}
                        {% endfor %}
                      {% elif task.file.eml_data and task.file.eml_data.header.received %}
                        {% for received in task.file.eml_data.header.received %}
                          {% if 'from' in received %}
                            <span>{{ received.from[0] }}</span> <small class="text-muted">{{ received.from[1] }}</small><br/>
                          {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                      {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% if current_user.role.can(action.download_images) %}
                    <tr id="email-body">
                      <th>Body</th>
                      <td>
                        <div class="row preview-done {% if not task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}" id="previews_images">
                          {% include 'previews.html' %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="row preview-wait {% if task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                          <div class="img-thumbnail small-status-flag status-flag-error">Content preview is not available</div>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endif %}
                  </table>

                  <!-- Image preview -->
                  {% elif current_user.role.can(action.download_images) %}
                  <div class="row preview-done {% if not task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}" id="previews_images">
                    {% include 'previews.html' %}
                  </div>
                  <div class="row preview-wait {% if task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                    <div class="img-thumbnail small-status-flag status-flag-error">Content preview is not available</div>
                  </div>
                  {% endif %}
                  {% if task.file.is_html %}
                    <div class="row">
                    {% if 'lookyloo' in task.reports and 'permaurl' in task.reports['lookyloo'].details %}
                      <a href="{{task.reports['lookyloo'].details['permaurl']}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">See capture on Lookyloo</a>
                    {% elif 'lookyloo' in task.reports and task.reports['lookyloo'].status == status.MANUAL %}
                      This document can probably be opened in a browser,
                      you can submit it to lookyloo and see.
                      Note that as it is sending the sample to a 3rd party service,
                      the module needs to be triggered manually.
                      <a href="{{url_for('manual_trigger_worker', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, worker_name='lookyloo')}}">
                          Click here to do so.
                      </a>
                    {% endif %}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {% if current_user.role.can(action.see_text_preview) %}
              {% if task.file.text %}
              <!-- Text Preview -->
              <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="text-preview-content">
                <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                  <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h3>Appercu text</h3>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row preview-done {% if not task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                  <div>The text content can be huge, only display a part of it.</div>
                  <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="img-hover">
                      <a href="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='txt_preview') }}" target="_blank">
                        <img class="img-thumbnail" width="70%" src="{{ url_for('api_task_download', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, source='txt_preview') }}">
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row preview-wait {% if task.file.previews|length %} d-none {%endif%}">
                  <div>Creating preview, please wait...</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            {% endif %}

            <!-- Text content -->
            {% if current_user.role.can('download_text') and task.file.text %}
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="text-content">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>Text content</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <pre>{{task.file.text}}</pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if task.file.metadata %}
            <!-- File metadata -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="metadata">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>Metadata</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12" style="margin-bottom:50px">
                  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered" >
                  {% for key, value in task.file.metadata.items() %}
                    <tr>
                      <th style="width:30%">{{key}}</th>
                      <td>{{value}}</td>
                    </tr>
                  {% endfor %}
                  </table>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <!-- Observables -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="observables_list">
              <div id="observables_content"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Extracted tasks -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="extracted">
                <div id="extracted_content"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Linked tasks -->
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane {% if not task.linked_tasks%} d-none {% endif %}" id="history">
              <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h3>History</h3>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
                  <tr>
                    <th>Date</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                  </tr>
                  {% for linked_task in task.linked_tasks %}
                  <tr class="{% if linked_task.uuid == task.uuid %}active{% endif %}" id="linkedTaskRow-{{ linked_task.uuid }}">
                    <td>
                      {{ moment(linked_task.save_date).format('L LT [UTC]Z') }}
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <a href="{{ url_for('api_analysis', task_id=linked_task.uuid) }}">
                        {{ render_icon(task.file.icon) }}
                        {{ linked_task.file.client_name }}
                      </a>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      {{ display_task_status(task.status, status) }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  {% endfor %}
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal notify -->
  {% if current_user.role.can('notify_cert') %}
    <div id="notifyModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <form id="notifyForm" class="form-horizontal" action="{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='notify') }}"
              onsubmit="return analysis.notify($(this).attr('action'))">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h4 class="modal-title">Send message to {{admin_name}}</h4>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4"><span><b>Your email address:</b></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-8"><input style="width:100%" name="email" type="email" id="email" required/></div>
              </div>
              <div class="row" style="margin-top:10px">
                <div class="col-md-4"><span><b>Your message:</b></span></div>
                <div class="col-md-8"><textarea name="message" required rows="10" style="width:100%" id="message"></textarea></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- boat fields -->
            <label class="boatymcboat form-label" for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input class="boatymcboat" autocomplete="off" type="text" id="name" name="name"
                   placeholder="Your fav boat name here">
            <!-- end -->
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
              <div class="col-md-10 d-none alert alert-info" id="notifySuccess">Your message has been correctly sent.</div>
              <div class="col-md-10 d-none alert alert-danger" id="notifyError">
                An error has occurred while sending your message:<span id="notifyErrorReason"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-1"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Cancel</button>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="notifySubmit">Send message</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Modal share -->
  {% if current_user.role.can('share_analysis') %}
    <div id="shareModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <h4 class="modal-title">Get a URL to share</h4>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <form id="shareForm" class="form-horizontal"
                    action="{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_task_action', task_id=task.uuid, seed=seed, action='share') }}"
                    onsubmit="return analysis.share($(this).attr('action'))">
              <div class="row g-3 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-auto">
                  <label for="shareDays" class="col-form-label">Expiration de l'URL:</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                  <input style="width:100px" class="form-control" aria-describedby="shareDaysHelp"
                                                                  id="shareDays" name="number" type="number" min="0" value="{{default_share_time}}" required>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                  <span id="shareDaysHelp" class="form-text">
                    en jours, 0 signifie pas d'expiration.
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary" id="shareBuild" style="float: right;">Create a shareable link</button>
              </form>

              </br>

              <div class="row">
                <div class="col d-none alert alert-info" id="shareSuccess">
                  Cette analyse est disponible à <b><span id="sharePeriod"></span></b> cette
                  <a href="" id="shareLink" class="alert-link">addresse</a> -
                  <button type="button" class="btn alert-link" style="padding:0"
                          title="Copy to clipboard"
                          onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(shareLink).then(
                                    function() {document.getElementById('copySuccess').classList.remove('d-none')},
                                    function() {document.getElementById('copyError').classList.remove('d-none')})">
                      (copier dans le presse-papier {{ render_icon('clipboard-plus', color='black') }})
                  </button>
                </div>
                <div class="col d-none alert alert-danger" id="shareError">
                  An error has occurred while creating the shareable link:
                  <span id="shareErrorReason"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col d-none alert alert-success" id="copySuccess">
                Le lien a été copié avec succès dans le presse-papier.
              </div>
              <div class="col d-none alert alert-danger" id="copyError">
                Unable to copy the sharing link to the clipboard.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary d-none" data-bs-dismiss="modal" id="closeBuild">Close</button>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
{% endblock %}

```

`website/web/templates/base.html`:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html  lang="en">
  <head>
    {% block head %}
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="icon" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='images/logo.svg') }}" type="image/svg+xml"
          integrity="{{get_sri('static/images', 'logo.svg')}}"
          crossorigin="anonymous">

    {{ moment.include_moment(local_js='/static/js/lib/moment-with-locales.min.js',
                             sri=get_sri('static/js/lib', 'moment-with-locales.min.js')) }}
    {% block styles %}
    <!-- Included stylesheets -->
    {{ bootstrap.load_css() }}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/style.css') }}"
          integrity="{{get_sri('static/css', 'style.css')}}"
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/ribbon.css') }}"
          integrity="{{get_sri('static/css', 'ribbon.css')}}"
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/lib/datatables.css') }}"
         {{get_sri('static/css/lib', 'datatables.css')}}
          crossorigin="anonymous">

    {% set overrides_css = load_custom_css('overrides.css') %}
    {% if overrides_css %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ overrides_css[0] }}"
          integrity="{{ overrides_css[1] }}"
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    {% endif %}
    {% endblock %}

    <title>{% block title %}Pandora{% endblock %}</title>
    {% endblock %}
  </head>

  <body>
    {% include "custom_header.html" ignore missing %}
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-light bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ url_for('api_root') }}">
          <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='images/logo-h.svg') }}" style="width:250px;" alt="PANDORA"
               integrity="{{get_sri('static/images', 'logo-h.svg')}}"
               crossorigin="anonymous">
        </a>

        <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
            <ul class="navbar-nav mx-5">
                {% if current_user.role.can([action.list_all_tasks, action.list_own_tasks], 'or') %}
                    <li id="tasks-nav" class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('api_tasks') }}">Recent</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}

                {% if current_user.role.can('submit_file') %}
                    <li id="submit-nav" class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('api_submit_page') }}">Submit</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if current_user.role.can('list_users') %}
                    <li class="nav-item" id="roles-nav">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('api_roles') }}">Roles</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if current_user.role.can('list_users') %}
                    <li class="nav-item" id="users-nav">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('api_users') }}">Users</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if current_user.role.can('manage_observables_lists') %}
                    <li class="nav-item" id="stats-nav">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('observables_lists') }}">Observables lists</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if current_user.role.can('list_stats') %}
                    <li class="nav-item" id="stats-nav">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('api_stats') }}">Statistics</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if current_user.is_admin %}
                    <li class="nav-item" id="admin-nav">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ url_for('api_admin_page') }}">Admin</a>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
            </ul>
            <ul class="navbar-nav mx-5">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <div onclick="toggle_detailed_view()">
                  <div class="form-check form-switch">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" value=""
                           id="detailedView" {% if current_user.detailed_view %}checked{% endif %}>
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="detailedView">
                      Detailed view
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% if show_project_page %}
      <div class="corner-ribbon top-right sticky bg-light shadow">
        <a href="https://github.com/pandora-analysis">Project page</a>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </nav>

    <div class="container-fluid">
      {% block content %}{% endblock %}
    </div>

    {% include "custom_footer.html" ignore missing %}

    {% block scripts %}
    <!-- Included scripts -->
    {{ bootstrap.load_js() }}
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/lib/jquery.min.js') }}"
            integrity="{{get_sri('static/js/lib', 'jquery.min.js')}}"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src='{{ url_for('static', filename='js/lib/datatables.js') }}'
           {{get_sri('static/js/lib', 'datatables.js')}}
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src='{{ url_for('static', filename='js/render_tables.js') }}'
            {{get_sri('static/js', 'render_tables.js')}}
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    {% set overrides_js = load_custom_js('overrides.js') %}
    {% if overrides_js %}
    <script src="{{  overrides_js[0] }}"
            integrity="{{ overrides_js[1] }}"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    {% endif %}
    <script>
        function toggle_detailed_view() {
            fetch("{{ url_for('api_toggle_detailed_view') }}", {
                  method: 'POST', // or 'PUT'
                  headers: {"X-CSRF-Token": "{{ csrf_token() }}"},
            })
              .then((response) => response.json())
              .then((data) => {
                      console.log('Success:', data);
                      window.location.reload(true);
                    })
              .catch((error) => {
                      console.error('Error:', error);
                    });
        }
    </script>

    {% endblock %}

  </body>
</html>

```

```html
  <div>
    <span class="h3">{{worker_meta.name}}</span>
    <span style="vertical-align:top;" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="{{worker_meta.description}}">{{render_icon('question-circle')}}</span>
  </div>

  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
    <tr>
      <th scope="row" style="width:30%">Status</th>
      <td>
        {{ display_status_badge(report.status, status) }}
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% if report.details %}
    <tr>
      <th scope="row" style="width:30%">Details</th>
      <td>
        <table class="table table-striped">
          {% for key, value in report.details.items() %}
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">{{key}}</th>
            <td>
            {% if value is string %}
              {{value}}
            {% elif value is mapping %}
            {% for k, v in value.items() %}
              {{k}} - {{v}}</br>
            {% endfor %}
            {% elif value is sequence %}
            {% for v in value %}
              {{v}}</br>
            {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
              {{value}}
            {% endif %}
            </td>
         </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
  </table>
</div>
```

`website/web/templates/macros.html`:

```html
{% macro display_status_badge(entry_status, status) %}
{% if entry_status == status.OVERWRITE %}
<span class="badge bg-secondary" title="Can't say, overwritten by admin.">
{% elif entry_status == status.ALERT %}
<span class="badge bg-danger" title="Consider this as malicious">
{% elif entry_status == status.WARN %}
<span class="badge bg-warning" title="Consider this as suspicious, act accordingly">
{% elif entry_status == status.CLEAN %}
<span class="badge bg-success" title="Consider it as clean, but check if any other module flag it as dangerous">
{% elif entry_status == status.ERROR %}
<span class="badge bg-dark" title="Something went wrong.">
{% elif entry_status in [status.DISABLED, status.NOTAPPLICABLE] %}
<span class="badge bg-secondary" title="Unable to determine the legitimacy">
{% endif %}
  {{ entry_status.name|lower }}
</span>
{% endmacro %}


{% macro display_task_status(task_status, status) %}
{% from 'bootstrap5/utils.html' import render_icon %}
<span class="img-thumbnail small-status-flag status-flag-{{ task_status.name.lower() }}">
{% if task_status == status.OVERWRITE %}
  {{ render_icon('question-octagon') }}
{% elif task_status == status.ERROR %}
  {{ render_icon('exclamation-octagon') }}
{% elif task_status == status.ALERT %}
  <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='images/skull.svg') }}" width = "15" height = "15">
{% elif task_status == status.WARN %}
{{ render_icon('exclamation-triangle') }}
{% elif task_status == status.CLEAN %}
{{ render_icon('check-circle') }}
{% else %}
  {{ render_icon('question') }}
{% endif %}
</span>
{% endmacro %}

```

`website/web/templates/observables_list.html`:

```html
{% from 'bootstrap5/utils.html' import render_icon %}
{% from "macros.html" import display_status_badge %}

<div class="row" style="margin-bottom:30px">
```
