```html
    <h3>Observables</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered" id="observablesTaskRows">
    <tr>
      <th>Status</th>
      <th>Type</th>
      <th>Observable</th>
      <th>Warninglists</th>
    </tr>
    {% for observable in task.observables %}
    <tr id="observableRow-{{ observable.sha256 }}">
      <td style="width:115px">
        {{ display_status_badge(observable.status, status) }}
      </td>
      <td style="width: 110px">
				{{ observable.observable_type }}
      </td>
      <td style="max-width: 400px">
        <div style="word-wrap: break-word">{{observable.value}}</div>
        {% if lookyloo_url and observable.observable_type == "url" %}
        <div style="float:right" id="lookyloo_submit-{{observable.sha256}}" class="btn alert-link"
             onclick="lookyloo('{{lookyloo_url}}', '{{observable.sha256}}', '{{observable.value}}')">
          Submit to Lookyloo
        </div>
        <a style="float:right;display:none" id='lookyloo_link-{{observable.sha256}}'
           class="btn alert-link" target="_blank" href=''>
          See capture on lookyloo
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      </td>
      <td style="max-width: 300px">
        <ul>
        {% for wl in observable.warninglists%}
          <li>{{wl.name}}</li>
        {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </table>
</div>
```

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}
```

```html
    Pandora - roles

{% block scripts %}
  {{ super() }}
  <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/role.js') }}"
          integrity="{{get_sri('static/js', 'role.js')}}"
          crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script>
      var pandoraRole = new Role("{{ csrf_token() }}", "{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_role', action='update') }}", "{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_role', action='reload') }}");
  </script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <table class="table table-hover">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="text-nowrap">Name</th>
        {% for key in action.__members__.keys() %}
        <th class="text-center">{{ key }}</th>
        {% endfor %}
      </tr>
    </thead>

    <tbody>
    {% for role in roles %}
      <tr id="row-{{ role.name }}">
        <th class="text-nowrap" scope="row" title="{{ role.description }}">{{ role.name.name }}</th>
        {% for action, perm in role.actions.items() %}
        <td class="text-center">
            <span class="badge bg-success {% if not perm %} d-none {% endif %}"
                  id="true-{{ role.name.name }}-{{ action.name }}" onclick="pandoraRole.update('{{ role.name.name }}', '{{ action.name }}', 0)">
                TRUE
            </span>
            <span class="badge bg-danger{% if perm %} d-none {% endif %}"
                  id="false-{{ role.name.name }}-{{ action.name }}" onclick="pandoraRole.update('{{ role.name.name }}', '{{ action.name }}', 1)">
                FALSE
            </span>
        </td>
        {% endfor %}
      </tr>
    {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="text-center">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="pandoraRole.reload()">Reload roles from config file</button>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
```

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}

{% block styles %}
  {{ super() }}
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/lib/dropzone.css') }}" type="text/css"
        integrity="{{get_sri('static/css/lib', 'dropzone.css')}}"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container">
  <div class="mb-3">
    {% if show_project_page %}
    <center>
      <h4>Pandora opens the box, so you don't have to!</h4>
    </center>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  <div class="mb-3">
    {% if special_disclaimer %}
    <center>

      {{special_disclaimer}}
    </div>
    </center>
    {% endif %}
  </div>


  <div class="md-3" onclick="toggle_password()">
    <div class="form-check form-switch">
      <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" value="" id="checkPassword">
      <label class="form-check-label" for="checkPassword">
        The file is password protected
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g-3 align-items-center d-none" id="enable-password">
    <div class="col-auto">
      <label for="encryption-password" class="col-form-label">Password</label>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="encryption-password" placeholder="String to use to decrypt the submission">
     </div>
  </div>
  </br>

  <div class="md-3" id="dropzone">
    <div class="dz-message" data-dz-message>
      <span><h2>Upload file, document, email or other</h2></span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="previews"></div>

  {% if current_user.detailed_view %}
  <div class="md-3">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="$('#workers-selection').toggleClass('d-none');">Advanced</button>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="md-3 d-none" id="workers-selection">
      <table class="table table-striped table-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th scope="col">Module</th>
            <th scope="col">Description</th>
            <th scope="col">Enable?</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {% for worker_name, worker_config in workers.items() %}
          {% if worker_config.meta.replicas > 0 %}
          <tr>
            <td>{{ worker_config.meta.name }}</td>
            <td>{{ worker_config.meta.description }}</td>
            <td><input type="checkbox" name="{{ worker_name }}"
                {% if worker_config.settings.required or worker_config.settings.run_by_default %}checked{%endif%}
                {% if worker_config.settings.required %}disabled{%endif%}
                />
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

  <div class="md-3" style="font-size:12px">
    <center>
      <div class="alert alert-light" role="alert">
        <strong>DISCLAIMER</strong><br/>
        {{generic_disclaimer | safe}}
      </div>
    </center>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- HTML heavily inspired by http://blueimp.github.io/jQuery-File-Upload/ -->
<div class="table table-striped" class="files" id="previews">

  <div id="template" class="file-row">
    <!-- This is used as the file preview template -->
    <div>
        <div class="dz-filename"><p class="name" data-dz-name></p></div>
        <div class="dz-error-message"><strong class="error text-danger" data-dz-errormessage></strong></div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="size" data-dz-size></p>
        <div class="progress active" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" aria-valuenow="0" aria-label="Uploading file">
          <div class="progress-bar bg-info" style="width:0%;" data-dz-uploadprogress></div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
{{ super() }}
<script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/lib/dropzone-min.js') }}"
        integrity="{{get_sri('static/js/lib', 'dropzone-min.js')}}"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/submit.js') }}"
        integrity="{{get_sri('static/js', 'submit.js')}}"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
  // Get the template HTML and remove it from the document.
  var previewNode = document.querySelector("#template");
  previewNode.id = "";
  var previewTemplate = previewNode.parentNode.innerHTML;
  previewNode.parentNode.removeChild(previewNode);
  $("div#dropzone").dropzone({
    url: "{{ url_for('PandoraAPI_api_submit') }}",
    headers: {"X-CSRF-Token": "{{ csrf_token() }}"},
    paramName: "file",
    maxFilesize: {{ max_file_size }}, // MB
    // maxFiles: 1,
    previewTemplate: previewTemplate,
    previewsContainer: "#previews", // Define the container to display the previews
    sending: function(file, xhr, formData) {
      formData.append("workersDisabled", getDisabledWorkers());
      formData.append("password", getPassword());
    },
    success: function(file, answer){
      window.setTimeout(function(){
        window.location = `/analysis/${answer.taskId}`;
      }, 100);
    },
    error: function(file, message){
      if (file.previewElement) {
        file.previewElement.classList.add("dz-error");
        if (typeof message !== "string" && message.error) {
          message = message.error;
        }
        for (let node of file.previewElement.querySelectorAll(
          "[data-dz-errormessage]"
        )) {
          node.textContent = message;
        }
      }
      $("div#dropzone").hide();
      window.setTimeout(function(){
        window.location = `/submit`;
      }, 2000);
    },
  });
</script>

<script>
function toggle_password() {
  var checkBox = document.getElementById("checkPassword");
  var text = document.getElementById("enable-password");
  if (checkBox.checked == true){
    text.classList.remove("d-none");
  } else {
     text.classList.add("d-none");
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

```

```html
{% block styles %}

{% block content %}

        Le ficher est protégé par un mot de passe
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g-3 align-items-center d-none" id="enable-password">

    </div>

     </div>
  </div>
  </br>

  <div class="md-3" id="dropzone">
    <div class="dz-message" data-dz-message>
      <span><h2>Téléversez un fichier, document, email, ou autre.</h2></span>
    </div>
```

`website/web/templates/tasks.html`:

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}
{% from 'bootstrap5/utils.html' import render_icon %}
{% from "macros.html" import display_task_status %}

{% block title %}
    My tasks
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <table id="TasksTable" class="table table-hover table-responsive" style="width:100%"
         data-csrf= {{csrf_token()}}"">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Id</th>
        <th>Owner</th>
        <th>Date</th>
        <th>Status</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>SHA256</th>
        <th></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
  </table>
  {% if current_user.is_admin %}
  <script>
      function deleteFile(url, uid) {
          if (! confirm("Are you sure you want to delete this file ? That action is irreversible !")) {
              return false;
          }
          fetch(url, {
            method: "POST",
            headers: {
              "X-CSRF-Token": "{{ csrf_token() }}"
            }
          })
          .then(response => response.json())
          .then(data => {
            if (data.success === false) {
              throw new Error(data.error);
            }
            $(`[data-uid=${data.file_id}]`).attr("onclick", "").toggleClass("btn-default btn-danger").html('File deleted');
          })
          .catch((error) => {
            alert("An error has occurred while removing file : " + error);
          });
      };
  </script>
  {% endif %}

{% endblock %}

```

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}

{% block title %}
    Pandora - users
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <form action="{{ url_for('api_clear_users') }}">
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">Clear all sessions</button>
  </form>
  <table class="table table-hover">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th scope="col">Id</th>
        <th scope="col">Name</th>
        <th scope="col">Admin</th>
        <th scope="col">First seen</th>
        <th scope="col">Last seen</th>
        <th scope="col">Last Used IP</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    {% for user in users %}
      <tr id="row-{{ user.session_id }}">
        <td>{{ user.session_id }}</td>
        <td>{{ user.name }}</td>
        <td>
        {% if user.is_admin %}
          <span class="badge bg-success">TRUE</span>
        {% else %}
          <span class="badge bg-danger">FALSE</span>
        {% endif %}
        </td>
        <td>{{ moment(user.first_seen).format('lll') }}</td>
        <td>{{ moment(user.last_seen).format('lll') }}</td>
        <td>
        {% if user.last_ip is none %}
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark">NULL</span>
        {% else %}
          {{ user.last_ip }}
        {% endif %}
        </td>
      </tr>
    {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
{% endblock %}
```

`website/web/templates/virustotal.html`:

```html
{% from 'bootstrap5/utils.html' import render_icon %}
{% from "macros.html" import display_status_badge %}

<div class="col-md-12" id="{{worker_name}}">
  <div>
    <span class="h3">{{worker_meta.name}}</span>
    <span style="vertical-align:top;" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="{{worker_meta.description}}">{{render_icon('question-circle')}}</span>
  </div>

  <table class="table table-hover table-bordered">
    <tr>
      <th scope="row" style="width:30%">Status</th>
      <td>
        {{ display_status_badge(report.status, status) }}
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% if report.details %}
    <tr>
      <th scope="row" style="width:30%">Details</th>
      <td>
        <table class="table table-striped">
          {% for key, value in report.details.items() %}
          <tr>
            <th scope="row">{{key}}</th>
            <td>
            {% if key == 'permaurl' %}
              <a href="{{value}}">Show report on VirusTotal</a>
            {% elif value is string %}
              {{value}}
            {% elif value is mapping %}
            {% for k, v in value.items() %}
              {{k}} - {{v}}</br>
            {% endfor %}
            {% elif value is sequence %}
            {% for v in value %}
              {{v}}</br>
            {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
              {{value}}
            {% endif %}
            </td>
         </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
  </table>
</div>

```
